# Run artifacts. ch4_inventory_build()/CH4_inventory_build() create in/, out/
# and plots/ under whatever run_directory they're given; these patterns are
# anchored to the repo root so a run launched from here doesn't commit the
# multi-GB Zenodo/EPA/Census downloads it caches under in/.
#
# Anchoring matters: the golden fixtures deliberately mirror this layout
# (python/tests/golden/*/out/, python/tests/golden/*/in/) and MUST stay tracked,
# so do not turn these into unanchored `in/` / `out/` patterns.
/in/
/out/
/plots/
